707
01:13:22,248 --> 01:13:26,057
<b>And I heard your voice right now only briefly, but I'm much better.</b>

708
01:13:26,788 --> 01:13:29,657
<b>I can't even remember when I was sad.</b>

709
01:13:30,227 --> 01:13:32,657
<b>Even the voice by itself is effective.</b>

710
01:13:33,098 --> 01:13:34,357
<b>It's more than enough.</b>

711
01:13:34,697 --> 01:13:37,197
<b>You'll be all better once you see me.</b>

712
01:13:37,998 --> 01:13:39,168
<b>A full recovery.</b>

713
01:13:41,968 --> 01:13:43,567
<b>I'll have to see you soon.</b>

714
01:13:44,937 --> 01:13:46,638
<b>When can I see you?</b>

715
