<b>Tomorrow.</b>

716
01:13:52,977 --> 01:13:54,048
<b>See you tomorrow.</b>

717
01:13:56,817 --> 01:13:57,987
<b>Tomorrow.</b>

718
01:14:01,088 --> 01:14:02,128
<b>How nice.</b>

719
01:14:38,527 --> 01:14:41,798
<b>Once I get on the plane, I'll be in Korea in half a day.</b>

720
01:14:48,638 --> 01:14:50,638
<b>I'll be there in two hours.</b>

721
01:15:03,248 --> 01:15:05,117
<b>I'll be there in 15 minutes.</b>

722
01:15:42,128 --> 01:15:43,388
<b>You're here.</b>

723
01:15:45,128 --> 01:15:46,498
<b>I'm back.</b>

724
01:16:14,288 --> 01:16:16,628
<b>(Thank you for watching "A Piece of Your Mind")</b>

725
